{
  "stem": "23155.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And since this tank came and-- and the doors opened, we went to the side, and they-- the British started coming in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They had no idea that we were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It just happened that they took that little road from the main road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They came from Hanover.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You know, it was a fighting unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They came in, and there was this little road, so they started to investigate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And here they found this camp, and here they found this horror.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They were stunned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So I suppose they-- they-- they started talking to headquarters, what-- what they found.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the first thing they did, they put up showers for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And so we could, the ones who were walking around-- there were very few of us-- could take showers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They started taking people out, only the ones who were very ill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The soldiers, they're all covered up, like, you know, like you saw them when they went to the Gulf War.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "You know, they had all this-- everything covered up because they were afraid to catch typhoid from us, because there were so many lice and typhoid and things like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And you only could go out completely naked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So they put a stretcher down, and before you knew, you had 10 naked women there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But of course, they took it one after the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
